<div class="alert alert-info">
  In order to secure your ThoughtWorks Go server you can restrict its access by IP. If you do so, only clients from this IP will be able to access it.
</div>
<h1>
  Secure your ThoughtWorks Go server
</h1>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span3 offset3">
    <%= form_tag("/ip", :method => "get") do %>
    <%= label_tag(:ip, "Enter your IP") %>
    <%= text_field_tag(:ip, @user.secure_ip)  %>
    <%= submit_tag("Save", class:"btn btn-large btn-primary") %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
